# ============================================================
# Environment variables for Intelligent Candidate Discovery
# ============================================================
# Copy this file to `.env` for local development, OR add these
# variables in your Vercel project: Settings → Environment Variables.
#
# All variables below are SERVER-SIDE (used by TanStack Start
# server functions). Never prefix secrets with VITE_.
# ------------------------------------------------------------

# Lovable AI Gateway key — powers semantic candidate ranking
# (text embeddings via google/gemini-embedding-001).
#
# Without this key the app still runs, but ranking falls back
# to a basic lexical (keyword-overlap) scorer with no semantic
# understanding.
#
# Where to get it:
#   1. Open your project on https://lovable.dev
#   2. Project Settings → Secrets → copy LOVABLE_API_KEY
#      (it is auto-provisioned for every Lovable project)
#
# How to set on Vercel:
#   Vercel Dashboard → Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#   Name:  LOVABLE_API_KEY
#   Value: <paste the key>
#   Environments: Production, Preview, Development
#   Then redeploy.
LOVABLE_API_KEY=